<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_458_r2l17">Wır ~ dıe <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc .
                        Bekennen etc Vmb ſölıch ladung vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_458_r2l18">klag als <expan>Rupre<ex>cht</ex></expan> von
                        wölfrıng <expan>lantschr<ex>eiber</ex></expan> cʒu
                            <expan>Am<ex>m</ex>berg</expan> vor der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_458_r2l19">ſelben lantſchrann getan hat vnd tut / auf den Hamer
                        ʒu Pruk </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_458_r2l20">vnd auf alle dıe gut dıe wır vnd dıe
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan>
                        lantſchrann </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_458_r2l21">lıgent <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / Daʒ wır
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıenern <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Herlin
                        vnd <expan cert="unknown">C.</expan>. </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_458_r2l22">Beheim <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> g </del>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gancʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt
                        vnd macht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_458_r2l23">dıe <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> vnſre vnd
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>güt<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_458_r2l24">ſtat gen Jm ʒu
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> vnd
                            <expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex>tretten</expan> ʒu <expan>gewin<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        vnd ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_458_r2l27">verluſt vnd ʒu allem <add><ab facs="#facs_458_r2l25">rechten </ab></add> . Mıt <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> etc / ut
                                <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_458" id="228r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir die <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc. bekennen etc. umb sölich ladung
                        und klag, als <expan>Rupre<ex>cht</ex></expan> von Wölfring,
                                <expan>lantschr<ex>eiber</ex></expan> czu
                            <expan>Am<ex>m</ex>berg</expan>, vor der selben lantschrann getan hat
                        und tut auf den hamer zu Pruk und auf alle die gut, die wir und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
                        lantschrann ligent <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienern <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Herlin
                        und <expan cert="unknown">C.</expan> Beheim <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>gancze<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt
                        und macht, die <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> unsre und
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>güt<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> und an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat gen
                        im zu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> und <expan>zu
                                v<ex>er</ex>tretten</expan>, zu <expan>gewin<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                        zu verlust und zu allem <add>rechten</add>. Mit
                            <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan> etc. Ut
                        <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
